text:
But, um...! There's still a lot of areas
where we need to put effort into.

We completed this joint training camp,
but we're still only halfway there!
Oh, no, it's nothing like that...!
No, I want you to take this seriously.

Chiyoko might say something like,
"There are still areas for improvement", but...

Facing those areas head-on and
steadily moving forward, that's also a talent.
That's why I rely on Chiyoko.
